Livingroom with fireplace and sliding doors also leading to patio.  Exterior storage closet off patio. In-unit laundry. Garage space #87 included. HOA provides 2 resident parking tags and 2 guest parking tags, unassigned spaces. HOA will not allow more than 1 dog or any pets over 30lbs.
